00:48.867 --> 00:50.934
A prisoner wants to meet with you.

00:50.936 --> 00:52.235
Kyle Sullivan.

00:52.237 --> 00:54.437
Kyle Sullivan? Kyle
Sullivan's in prison?

00:54.439 --> 00:56.940
That is fantastic. I hope he fries.

00:58.309 --> 00:59.442
Who is Kyle Sullivan?

00:59.444 --> 01:01.578
He was your dad's fifth grade bully.

01:01.580 --> 01:02.912
You had a bully, Dad?

01:02.914 --> 01:05.281
You're like a giant.

01:05.283 --> 01:06.783
