braces, or had zits.

01:59.771 --> 02:01.471
What a fun point.

02:03.507 --> 02:05.074
Weren't you a huge bully, Stella?

02:05.076 --> 02:06.542
I wasn't a bully.

02:06.544 --> 02:09.345
