obviously still haunts you.

02:41.012 --> 02:43.913
Bad idea, Mike. Let the
past stay in the past.

02:43.915 --> 02:46.816
Don't go to see Kyle.
Trust me on this one.

02:46.818 --> 02:48.151
Well, I'm gonna go see him.

02:48.153 --> 02:51.054
